Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.02,Default,Yukko,0,0,0,,I'll take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（祐子）山を張ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.02,Default,Yukko,0,0,0,,Since I don't know what will be on the English test,
