Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:25.24,Default,Yukko,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（祐子）違うよ カゼだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（祐子の母）\N元気いっぱいじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.48,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You seem lively and healthy enough.
