Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.12,Default,Superintendant,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…というか 肝心の わらがない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.36,Default,Superintendant,0,0,0,,I don't even have the always important straw,
